ink: client.enableAutoSync(opts?)\" href=\"#clientenableautosyncopts\"\u003e\u003csvg class=\"octicon octicon-link\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" version=\"1.1\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" aria-hidden=\"true\"\u003e\u003cpath d=\"m7.775 3.275 1.25-1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1 4.95 4.95l-2.5 2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1-4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1 .018-1.042.751.751 0 0 1 1.042-.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l2.5-2.5a2.002 2.002 0 0 0-2.83-2.83l-1.25 1.25a.751.751 0 0 1-1.042-.018.751.751 0 0 1-.018-1.042Zm-4.69 9.64a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l1.25-1.25a.751.751 0 0 1 1.042.018.751.751 0 0 1 .018 1.042l-1.25 1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1-4.95-4.95l2.5-2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1-.018 1.042.751.751 0 0 1-1.042.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0-2.83 0l-2.5 2.5a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 0 2.83Z\"\u003e\u003c/path\u003e\u003c/svg\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003cp dir=\"auto\"\u003eEnable automatic background syncing (enabled by default).\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp dir=\"auto\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eReturns\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cul dir=\"auto\"\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003ccode\u003evoid\u003c/code\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\u003chr\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"markdown-heading\" dir=\"auto\"\u003e\u003ch3 tabindex=\"-1\" class=\"heading-element\" dir=\"auto\"\u003e\u003ccode\u003eclient.disableAutoSync()\u003c/code\u003e\u003c/h3\u003e\u003ca id=\"user-content-clientdisableautosync\" class=\"anchor\" aria-label=\"Permalink: client.disableAutoSync()\" href=\"#clientdisableautosync\"\u003e\u003csvg class=\"octicon octicon-link\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" version=\"1.1\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" aria-hidden=\"true\"\u003e\u003cpath d=\"m7.775 3.275 1.25-1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1 4.95 4.95l-2.5 2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1-4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1 .018-1.042.751.751 0 0 1 1.042-.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l2.5-2.5a2.002 2.002 0 0 0-2.83-2.83l-1.25 1.25a.751.751 0 0 1-1.042-.018.751.751 0 0 1-.018-1.042Zm-4.69 9.64a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l1.25-1.25a.751.751 0 0 1 1.042.018.751.751 0 0 1 .018 1.042l-1.25 1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1-4.95-4.95l2.5-2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1-.018 1.042.751.751 0 0 1-1.042.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0-2.83 0l-2.5 2.5a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 0 2.83Z\"\u003e\u003c/path\u003e\u003c/svg\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003cp dir=\"auto\"\u003eDisable AutoSync.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp dir=\"auto\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eReturns\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cul dir=\"auto\"\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003ccode\u003evoid\u003c/code\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\u003chr\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"markdown-heading\" dir=\"auto\"\u003e\u003ch3 tabindex=\"-1\" class=\"heading-element\" dir=\"auto\"\u003e\u003ccode\u003eclient.enableBackgroundStatusTracking()\u003c/code\u003e\u003c/h3\u003e\u003ca id=\"user-content-clientenablebackgroundstatustracking\" class=\"anchor\" aria-label=\"Permalink: client.enableBackgroundStatusTracking()\" href=\"#clientenablebackgroundstatustracking\"\u003e\u003csvg class=\"octicon octicon-link\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" version=\"1.1\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" aria-hidden=\"true\"\u003e\u003cpath d=\"m7.775 3.275 1.25-1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1 4.95 4.95l-2.5 2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1-4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1 .018-1.042.751.751 0 0 1 1.042-.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l2.5-2.5a2.002 2.002 0 0 0-2.83-2.83l-1.25 1.25a.751.751 0 0 1-1.042-.018.751.751 0 0 1-.018-1.042Zm-4.69 9.64a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l1.25-1.25a.751.751 0 0 1 1.042.018.751.751 0 0 1 .018 1.042l-1.25 1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1-4.95-4.95l2.5-2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1-.018 1.042.751.751 0 0 1-1.042.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0-2.83 0l-2.5 2.5a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 0 2.83Z\"\u003e\u003c/path\u003e\u003c/svg\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003cp dir=\"auto\"\u003eEnable background tracking. Recommended to call in your service worker.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cul dir=\"auto\"\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eWarms the cache with an initial refresh so \u003ccode\u003egetUser()\u003c/code\u003e is fast when the popup opens\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eSets up a message listener for the optional content script's checkout return notification\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\u003cp dir=\"auto\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eReturns\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cul dir=\"auto\"\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003ccode\u003evoid\u003c/code\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\u003chr\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"markdown-heading\" dir=\"auto\"\u003e\u003ch3 tabindex=\"-1\" class=\"heading-element\" dir=\"auto\"\u003e\u003ccode\u003eclient.getPlans()\u003c/code\u003e\u003c/h3\u003e\u003ca id=\"user-content-clientgetplans\" class=\"anchor\" aria-label=\"Permalink: client.getPlans()\" href=\"#clientgetplans\"\u003e\u003csvg class=\"octicon octicon-link\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" version=\"1.1\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" aria-hidden=\"true\"\u003e\u003cpath d=\"m7.775 3.275 1.25-1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1 4.95 4.95l-2.5 2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1-4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1 .018-1.042.751.751 0 0 1 1.042-.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l2.5-2.5a2.002 2.002 0 0 0-2.83-2.83l-1.25 1.25a.751.751 0 0 1-1.042-.018.751.751 0 0 1-.018-1.042Zm-4.69 9.64a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l1.25-1.25a.751.751 0 0 1 1.042.018.751.751 0 0 1 .018 1.042l-1.25 1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1-4.95-4.95l2.5-2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1-.018 1.042.751.751 0 0 1-1.042.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0-2.83 0l-2.5 2.5a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 0 2.83Z\"\u003e\u003c/path\u003e\u003c/svg\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003cp dir=\"auto\"\u003eFetch the list of plans configured for your app.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp dir=\"auto\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eReturns\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cul dir=\"auto\"\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003ccode\u003ePromise\u0026lt;PlanForSDK[]\u0026gt;\u003c/code\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\u003chr\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"markdown-heading\" dir=\"auto\"\u003e\u003ch2 tabindex=\"-1\" class=\"heading-element\" dir=\"auto\"\u003eTroubleshooting\u003c/h2\u003e\u003ca id=\"user-content-troubleshooting\" class=\"anchor\" aria-label=\"Permalink: Troubleshooting\" href=\"#troubleshooting\"\u003e\u003csvg class=\"octicon octicon-link\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" version=\"1.1\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" aria-hidden=\"true\"\u003e\u003cpath d=\"m7.775 3.275 1.25-1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1 4.95 4.95l-2.5 2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1-4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1 .018-1.042.751.751 0 0 1 1.042-.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l2.5-2.5a2.002 2.002 0 0 0-2.83-2.83l-1.25 1.25a.751.751 0 0 1-1.042-.018.751.751 0 0 1-.018-1.042Zm-4.69 9.64a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l1.25-1.25a.751.751 0 0 1 1.042.018.751.751 0 0 1 .018 1.042l-1.25 1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1-4.95-4.95l2.5-2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1-.018 1.042.751.751 0 0 1-1.042.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0-2.83 0l-2.5 2.5a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 0 2.83Z\"\u003e\u003c/path\u003e\u003c/svg\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"markdown-heading\" dir=\"auto\"\u003e\u003ch3 tabindex=\"-1\" class=\"heading-element\" dir=\"auto\"\u003e“My UI didn’t update after checkout”\u003c/h3\u003e\u003ca id=\"user-content-my-ui-didnt-update-after-checkout\" class=\"anchor\" aria-label=\"Permalink: “My UI didn’t update after checkout”\" href=\"#my-ui-didnt-update-after-checkout\"\u003e\u003csvg class=\"octicon octicon-link\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" version=\"1.1\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" aria-hidden=\"true\"\u003e\u003cpath d=\"m7.775 3.275 1.25-1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1 4.95 4.95l-2.5 2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1-4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1 .018-1.042.751.751 0 0 1 1.042-.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l2.5-2.5a2.002 2.002 0 0 0-2.83-2.83l-1.25 1.25a.751.751 0 0 1-1.042-.018.751.751 0 0 1-.018-1.042Zm-4.69 9.64a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l1.25-1.25a.751.751 0 0 1 1.042.018.751.751 0 0 1 .018 1.042l-1.25 1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1-4.95-4.95l2.5-2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1-.018 1.042.751.751 0 0 1-1.042.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0-2.83 0l-2.5 2.5a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 0 2.83Z\"\u003e\u003c/path\u003e\u003c/svg\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003cp dir=\"auto\"\u003eIn most cases the update will feel \u003cstrong\u003einstant\u003c/strong\u003e.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp dir=\"auto\"\u003eThat’s because Stripe typically reloads/redirects after payment, and when the user opens your extension again the SDK will fetch the latest status right away (and also revalidate in the background).\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp dir=\"auto\"\u003eIf the user \u003cstrong\u003ekeeps your extension UI open the whole time\u003c/strong\u003e (e.g. they pay in another tab and never close the popup/options page), the status will update when they next focus the popup (via AutoSync) or close/reopen it.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp dir=\"auto\"\u003eIf you want truly instant updates even while the extension UI stays open, you can add the optional content script build — but it’s optional on purpose:\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cul dir=\"auto\"\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eAdding a content script often triggers extra Chrome warnings and can make the review process take longer.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eBillingExtensionsSDK defaults to a no-content-script approach to reduce review friction.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"markdown-heading\" dir=\"auto\"\u003e\u003ch3 tabindex=\"-1\" class=\"heading-element\" dir=\"auto\"\u003e“Can i add a free trial period?”\u003c/h3\u003e\u003ca id=\"user-content-can-i-add-a-free-trial-period\" class=\"anchor\" aria-label=\"Permalink: “Can i add a free trial period?”\" href=\"#can-i-add-a-free-trial-period\"\u003e\u003csvg class=\"octicon octicon-link\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" version=\"1.1\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" aria-hidden=\"true\"\u003e\u003cpath d=\"m7.775 3.275 1.25-1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1 4.95 4.95l-2.5 2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1-4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1 .018-1.042.751.751 0 0 1 1.042-.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l2.5-2.5a2.002 2.002 0 0 0-2.83-2.83l-1.25 1.25a.751.751 0 0 1-1.042-.018.751.751 0 0 1-.018-1.042Zm-4.69 9.64a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l1.25-1.25a.751.751 0 0 1 1.042.018.751.751 0 0 1 .018 1.042l-1.25 1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1-4.95-4.95l2.5-2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1-.018 1.042.751.751 0 0 1-1.042.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0-2.83 0l-2.5 2.5a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 0 2.83Z\"\u003e\u003c/path\u003e\u003c/svg\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003cp dir=\"auto\"\u003eYes! With the latest version of the SDK, you can now add free trial periods to your applications!\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"markdown-heading\" dir=\"auto\"\u003e\u003ch3 tabindex=\"-1\" class=\"heading-element\" dir=\"auto\"\u003e“I’m seeing localhost URLs”\u003c/h3\u003e\u003ca id=\"user-content-im-seeing-localhost-urls\" class=\"anchor\" aria-label=\"Permalink: “I’m seeing localhost URLs”\" href=\"#im-seeing-localhost-urls\"\u003e\u003csvg class=\"octicon octicon-link\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" version=\"1.1\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" aria-hidden=\"true\"\u003e\u003cpath d=\"m7.775 3.275 1.25-1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1 4.95 4.95l-2.5 2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1-4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1 .018-1.042.751.751 0 0 1 1.042-.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l2.5-2.5a2.002 2.002 0 0 0-2.83-2.83l-1.25 1.25a.751.751 0 0 1-1.042-.018.751.751 0 0 1-.018-1.042Zm-4.69 9.64a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l1.25-1.25a.751.751 0 0 1 1.042.018.751.751 0 0 1 .018 1.042l-1.25 1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1-4.95-4.95l2.5-2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1-.018 1.042.751.751 0 0 1-1.042.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0-2.83 0l-2.5 2.5a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 0 2.83Z\"\u003e\u003c/path\u003e\u003c/svg\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003cp dir=\"auto\"\u003eIf your billing URL points to localhost in production:\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cul dir=\"auto\"\u003e\n\u003cli\u003everify the app/environment base URL configuration in your dashboard/backend,\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eand ensure you’re using the correct environment variables.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\u003chr\u003e\n\u003c/article\u003e","loaded":true,"timedOut":false,"errorMessage":null,"headerInfo":{"toc":[{"level":1,"text":"BillingExtensionsSDK","anchor":"billingextensionssdk","htmlText":"BillingExtensionsSDK"},{"level":2,"text":"Menu","anchor":"menu","htmlText":"Menu"},{"level":2,"text":"Secure server-side API (optional — the SDK works without this)","anchor":"secure-server-side-api-optional--the-sdk-works-without-this","htmlText":"Secure server-side API (optional — the SDK works without this)"},{"level":2,"text":"Important setup order (don’t skip this)","anchor":"important-setup-order-dont-skip-this","htmlText":"Important setup order (don’t skip this)"},{"level":2,"text":"Install","anchor":"install","htmlText":"Install"},{"level":3,"text":"Option A — npm (recommended)","anchor":"option-a--npm-recommended","htmlText":"Option A — npm (recommended)"},{"level":3,"text":"Init (recommended)","anchor":"init-recommended","htmlText":"Init (recommended)"},{"level":4,"text":"Quick start (works for any extension — no npm project required)","anchor":"quick-start-works-for-any-extension--no-npm-project-required","htmlText":"Quick start (works for any extension — no npm project required)"},{"level":4,"text":"Optional flags","anchor":"optional-flags","htmlText":"Optional flags"},{"level":3,"text":"Option B — drop in the dist file (no npm / no build step)","anchor":"option-b--drop-in-the-dist-file-no-npm--no-build-step","htmlText":"Option B — drop in the dist file (no npm / no build step)"},{"level":2,"text":"Before you start: required Chrome permissions - (already done if you ran the init script)","anchor":"before-you-start-required-chrome-permissions---already-done-if-you-ran-the-init-script","htmlText":"Before you start: required Chrome permissions - (already done if you ran the init script)"},{"level":2,"text":"Quick start (MV3 service worker) - (already done if you ran the init script)","anchor":"quick-start-mv3-service-worker---already-done-if-you-ran-the-init-script","htmlText":"Quick start (MV3 service worker) - (already done if you ran the init script)"},{"level":2,"text":"Using the SDK","anchor":"using-the-sdk","htmlText":"Using the SDK"},{"level":3,"text":"Gating paid features","anchor":"gating-paid-features","htmlText":"Gating paid features"},{"level":3,"text":"Listening for updates","anchor":"listening-for-updates","htmlText":"Listeni